{"tid":534952,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"基沙文與巴塞達成協議，明夏加盟","createTime":"2018-01-20T10:47:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-20T11:09:54.000Z","uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"84612222954286ab4b8d349627c43d270de2c0b1","tid":534952,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T10:47:09.000Z","msg":"根據《每日體育報》消息稱，巴塞和基沙文達成了一致，球員將在今夏加盟，並且雙方同意了一項違約條款，即任何一方違背原本的約定，那麼就要支付另一方相應的賠償金。  報導還表示巴塞會將會為他保留7號球衣。讓他在夏天加盟之後，可以繼續自己在馬體會時所穿的號碼。等到夏天球員的違約金會變成1億歐元，而1億歐元對於現時的轉會市場，不會是一個昂貴價錢。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好撚癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5265e0e3eb0d5ad80393af23097ceafb4dbf53eb","tid":534952,"uid":7729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T10:55:37.000Z","msg":"又係疤狗報煩撚住晒"},{"pid":"07f007fc4d3e1b2435756eb1e8fa2e0a4f66cae7","tid":534952,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T10:55:55.000Z","msg":"唔撚係掛真係買？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n要帶bar男好過，完全唔知電話佬邊忽勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba97b2a29bec406ad8b5e90cbdc6d3723cfb6a64","tid":534952,"uid":12034,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T10:59:26.000Z","msg":"1億歐? <br />\n想賺多筆簽字費都唔係咁賺呀<br />\n去2日就比我獌買走"},{"pid":"8a1cda13bda6d69e242e2733595de20c03df30ac","tid":534952,"uid":14350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07f007fc4d3e1b2435756eb1e8fa2e0a4f66cae7","tid":534952,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T10:55:55.000Z","msg":"唔撚係掛真係買？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\